rong></li><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/Instance\"><code>WebAssembly.Instance</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/Memory\"><code>WebAssembly.Memory</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/Table\"><code>WebAssembly.Table</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/CompileError\"><code>WebAssembly.CompileError</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/LinkError\"><code>WebAssembly.LinkError</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/RuntimeError\"><code>WebAssembly.RuntimeError</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong>Vererbung:</strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Eigenschaften</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/constructor\"><code>Object.prototype.constructor</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/proto\"><code>Object.prototype.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Methoden</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Die&nbsp;<strong><code>WebAssembly.compile()</code></strong>&nbsp;Funktion kompiliert ein&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/Module\"><code>WebAssembly.Module</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> aus WebAssembly Binärcode. Hilfreich ist diese Funktion, um ein Modul zu kompilieren, bevor es instanziiert werden kann&nbsp;(Andernfalls sollte die <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/instantiate\"><code>WebAssembly.instantiate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Funktion verwendet werden).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">Promise&lt;WebAssembly.Module&gt; WebAssembly.compile(bufferSource);</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameter","title":"Parameter","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"buffersource\"><em>bufferSource</em></dt>\n <dd>Ein&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Typed_arrays\">typisiertes Array</a> oder&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer\">ArrayBuffer</a>,&nbsp;das&nbsp;den Binärcode des zu kompilierenden .wasm Moduls enthält.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"rückgabewert","title":"Rückgabewert","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Ein&nbsp;<code>Promise</code>, das sich in ein <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/Module\"><code>WebAssembly.Module</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> kompiliertes Objekt auflöst.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"fehlerbehandlung","title":"Fehlerbehandlung","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Wenn&nbsp;<code>bufferSource</code> kein&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Typed_arrays\">typisiertes Array</a>&nbsp;ist, wird ein&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypeError\"><code>TypeError</code></a> geworfen.</li>\n <li>Wenn die Kompilierung fehlschlägt, wird das Promise mit einem&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/CompileError\"><code>WebAssembly.CompileError</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> verworfen.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Das folgende Beispiel kompiliert den geladenen simple.wasm Bytecode unter Verwendung der&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: -0.00278rem;\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: -0.00278rem;\">compile()</code><span style=\"font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: -0.00278rem;\">&nbsp;Funktion und sendet ihn an einen&nbsp;</span><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\" style=\"font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: -0.00278rem;\">Web Worker</a><span style=\"font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: -0.00278rem;\"> mittels&nbsp;</span><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Worker/postMessage\" style=\"font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: -0.00278rem;\">postMessage()</a><span style=\"font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: -0.00278rem;\">.</span></p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> worker <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Worker</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"wasm_worker.js\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">fetch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'simple.wasm'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">response</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span>\n  response<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">arrayBuffer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">bytes</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span>\n  WebAssembly<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">compile</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>bytes<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">mod</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span>\n  worker<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">postMessage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>mod<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>Hinweis</strong>: Du wirst wahrscheinlich in den meisten Fällen <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/compileStreaming\"><code>WebAssembly.compileStreaming()</code></a> verwenden wollen, da es effizienter als&nbsp;<code>compile()</code>&nbsp;arbeitet.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://webassembly.github.io/spec/js-api/#webassemblycompile\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">WebAssembly JavaScript Interface<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'compile()' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Arbeitsentwurf</span></td>\n   <td>Initial draft definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.WebAssembly.compile","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/compile/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/WebAssembly\">WebAssembly</a> Übersichtsseite</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/WebAssembly/Concepts\">WebAssembly concepts</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/WebAssembly/Using_the_JavaScript_API\">Using the WebAssembly JavaScript API</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beispiele","id":"beispiele"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Die WebAssembly.compile() Funktion kompiliert ein WebAssembly.Module (en-US) aus WebAssembly Binärcode. Hilfreich ist diese Funktion, um ein Modul zu kompilieren, bevor es instanziiert werden kann (Andernfalls sollte die WebAssembly.instantiate() (en-US) Funktion verwendet werden).","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WebAssembly.compile()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"WebAssembly.compile()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"WebAssembly.compile()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"WebAssembly.compile()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"WebAssembly.compile()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"WebAssembly.compile()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/webassembly/compile","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/webassembly/compile/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"JavaScript-Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"Globale Objekte"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly","title":"WebAssembly"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/compile","title":"WebAssembly.compile()"}],"pageTitle":"WebAssembly.compile() - JavaScript | MDN","noIndexing":false}}